'''Annette''' is a member of a mommy group Violet briefly joined.

==History==
Annette and her daughter Daisy, were part of a mommy group with [[Lynn (Deal With It)|Lynn]] and her son Truman and [[Trish (Deal With It)|Trish]] and her son Leo. Violet joined their group with Lucas. Violet was shocked to learn that Lynn had only recently stopped breastfeeding her three year old and was co-sleeping with him. And pointed out that Trish's son, Leo, biting wasn't a phase because he was over the age of three. After their first meeting, none of the others would return Violet's phone calls.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She has a daughter named Daisy.
